parameters: \C[23][Luna]\C[0] This place is...
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] This is... this orb of light is...
"Turn back now."
"The enemy is too formidable. Not even a miracle could occur."
heroine_1
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Who are you?
"It doesn't matter who. Retreat."
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] No. If we leave them be, who knows who will be killed next.
"I cannot stand by and watch you die."
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] We won't know unless we try.
"I understand. That's why I've come to stop you."
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] You won't know the outcome unless you fight, right?
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] You... who are you?
"It doesn't matter. Just a passing orb of light."
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] I see... Now I'm certain. You're Regnus Grahardt.
"No."

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Yes, you are Regnus Grahardt. The servant, no... Luca said, "I met
Regnus Grahardt."

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Regnus Grahardt, there must be a reason you can't reveal your
identity. A reason why you want to help us but can't.
Regnus Grahardt: It seems hiding it is futile.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] I thought so. But I can't heed that advice.

Regnus Grahardt: If you insist on fighting Lucia and the others, then
I ask you to wait a little longer.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Wait? For whom? How long?
Regnus Grahardt: I can't say more. Just wait a little longer.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] "The Mirror of Truth"...
Regnus Grahardt: ...!
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] The reason to wait was told by "The Mirror of Truth," wasn't it?
other/takibi-kaisou
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] One is about the Knights of Messiah, Lord Ceres and the others.
other/kaisou-a3
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] The second is the mysterious girl who was shouting.
other/rei-kaisou1

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] The third is the apprentice sorcerer who passed the baptism of
Valentina.
other/rei-kaisou2
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] You said her name was "Rae Granford," right?
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Regnus Grahardt, you know these people.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Are you saying to wait until these people make their move?
heroine_1

Regnus Grahardt: Yes, I want you to wait until these people make their
move. If "The Mirror of Truth" has prophesied it, then...
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] I see... Even "The Mirror of Truth" is trying to stop me.
Regnus Grahardt: ...

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Sorry, but I can't wait. I absolutely hate the idea of that happening
again... Something irreversible could happen while we're waiting. I
can't afford to wait calmly anymore.
Regnus Grahardt: ...
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] But Lady Rade could wait.

Regnus Grahardt: Rade will not interfere with you. She is not an ally
to either side.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Then I have no choice but to do it myself.
Regnus Grahardt: Luna...
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Sorry, I can't heed your advice.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] See you. Lucia and the others are waiting.
heroine_2
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Regnus Grahardt, thank you for the magical box.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] I'll make a miracle happen that won't wake up.
Regnus Grahardt: ...
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Goodbye, Regnus Grahardt...
Regnus Grahardt: Luna...
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Thank you... for caring about me until the end. Bye now.
Regnus Grahardt: ...
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Everyone, it's going to be okay now.
\C[24][Becky]\C[0] Hey Luna, were you talking to someone?
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] No, it's nothing. Let's go.

events.name: レグナス・グラハード
